room_title: Escape room "Prison Break" by ZScape Games in Livermore
room_address: 2110 Omega Rd Suite E, San Ramon, CA 94583
room_description:
You've been thrown in jail for a crime you may or may not have committed. One thing's for certain, you don't plan on staying locked up for long...
Use the limited resources of your cell and some help from an alibi to escape before the Warden finds out what you're up to in Prison Break!
